{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT was asked to digest the contents of simulated ADAS and AV manuals and convey this information through a conversational, interactive medium that adapts to users' responses.",
    "The training content was developed by inputting manual descriptions into ChatGPT.",
    "This information was transformed into clear, conversational language suitable for learners even with little or no relevant technical backgrounds.",
    "By doing so, ChatGPT provided personalised guidance, clarified user queries, and verified understanding through targeted follow-up questions.",
    "This methodology was designed to impart knowledge and engage users in a two-way dialogue, fostering a deeper understanding of ADAS functionalities and enhancing the learning experience."
  ]
}